368
00:15:37,675 --> 00:15:38,850
Hey.

369
00:15:38,894 --> 00:15:40,374
Oh, please.Oh.

370
00:15:40,417 --> 00:15:42,376
Young lady.Thank you.

371
00:15:42,419 --> 00:15:44,639
