376
00:15:57,043 --> 00:15:59,001
Wait, easy, tiger.
Nobody's going anywhere.

377
00:15:59,045 --> 00:16:00,350
No?Dinner's on me. Remember?

378
00:16:00,394 --> 00:16:01,786
Yeah.

379
00:16:01,830 --> 00:16:04,354
So, when I was maybe,
