00:16:14,060 --> 00:16:15,887
And when it got dark,
we got in our sleeping bags

385
00:16:15,931 --> 00:16:17,237
and we went to sleep.

386
00:16:17,280 --> 00:16:20,370
And it was the middle
of the night. It was so dark.

387
00:16:20,414 --> 00:16:23,373
And we were
in the middle of nowhere.

388
00:16:23,417 --> 00:16:25,027
That's when I heard it.Hmm?

389
00:16:25,071 --> 00:16:27,203
The rain.[chuckles]

390
00:16:27,247 --> 00:16:29,379
I mean, it was pelting our tent.

391
00:16:29,423 --> 00:16:31,816
And I thought, for sure, this
