392
00:16:31,860 --> 00:16:34,123
And then,
the lightning.

393
00:16:34,167 --> 00:16:35,646
One minute,
it's like 12:00 noon,

394
00:16:35,690 --> 00:16:37,953
and the next,
it is completely black.

395
00:16:37,997 --> 00:16:40,129
And then, the thunder.
[imitates thunder]

396
00:16:40,173 --> 00:16:42,262
I mean, it was
like bombs dropping.

397
00:16:42,305 --> 00:16:44,264
And what about your dad?

398
00:16:44,307 --> 00:16:46,701
What was he doing
during all of this?

399
00:16:46,744 --> 00:16:48,529
My dad?

400
00:16:48,572 --> 00:16:51,140
My dad was laughing.

401
00:16:51,184 --> 00:16:53,273
Roaring.

402
00:16:53,316 --> 00:16:55,275
"How about that God?" he said.

403
00:16:55,318 --> 00:16:57,277
"Can he put on a show or what?"

